<a name="introduction"></a> 1. Introduction

This document provides a unified, de-duplicated, system-wide technical specification for the Lifepreneur Admin Dashboard and supporting application infrastructure. It merges and synthesizes all material from the previously separate audits:

Full Audit (overall system inventory)

Phase 1 (Data model and schema audit)

Phase 2 (Admin API and permission logic)

Phase 3 (UI architecture and component library)

Phase 4 (Analytics/KPI layer)

Phase 5 (Subscription lifecycle and notifications)

The purpose of this specification is to describe the current state, desired state, and functional expectations of the admin subsystem in a format suitable for a model (Claude) to use as the basis for generating actionable implementation plans.

This document is intentionally descriptive, not prescriptive—it outlines system behavior, structures, components, and logic without providing direct implementation commands.

